Package org.github.fussel178.telestion.extension.corfu.corfu.mapper.message

Interface CorfuPayload

All Superinterfaces:
CorfuStruct, de.wuespace.telestion.api.message.JsonMessage
All Known Subinterfaces:
AppTelecommandPayload, AppTelemetryPayload
public interface CorfuPayload extends CorfuStruct
Represents a generic payload of a Corfu application. This interface acts as a root for the specializations AppTelemetryPayload and AppTelecommandPayload. Actual Corfu payloads should implement the specializations in favor of this root interface.

    • nodeId

      short nodeId()
      Returns the associated node id. This is needed because standard telemetry have different origins as nodes run different applications and therefore send different standard telemetry. Only one application (running on the node) "packs" the standard telemetry and sends them to ground. This parameter specifies if the payload is a node specific payload and which node is associated.

      Note: Return ANY_NODE_ID if the payload is not associated to any particular node.
